    </RadzenColumn>
</RadzenRow>
<RadzenText TextStyle="TextStyle.Subtitle2" TagName="TagName.H4" class="rz-mt-5">Responsive ordering</RadzenText>
<RadzenText TextStyle="TextStyle.Body2">You can reorder columns on different screen sizes. Resize your browser window to see how the columns reorder. See <a href="/breakpoints">Breakpoints</a> to learn more.</RadzenText>
