<RadzenText TextStyle="TextStyle.Body1" TagName="TagName.H4" class="rz-mt-5">By default, the spacing between columns is set to <code>1rem</code>, via the <code>--rz-gap</code> CSS variable. Spacing between coulmns can be controlled by setting the <code>Gap</code> property of the parent <code>RadzenRow</code> component.</RadzenText>
